highlights.text: Kendrick Lamar has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “All The Stars (with SZA)” is the highest at #2.
“King's Dead (with Kendrick Lamar, Future & James Blake)” by Jay Rock, Kendrick Lamar, Future, and James Blake is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 76 spots at #30.
“Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 60 weeks straight.
“Look Alive (feat. Drake)” by BlocBoy JB and Drake is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #11.
